README

Gentoo overlay from gentoo-italia (alessandro.rosetti@gmail.com)

1)
create "/etc/portage/repos.conf/gentoo-italia.conf"
change repo location if needed (/var/lib/repos/).
---------------------------------------------------
[DEFAULT]
main-repo = gentoo

[gentoo-italia]
location = /var/lib/repos/gentoo-italia
sync-type = git
sync-uri = https://github.com/hexvar/gentoo-italia
auto-sync = yes
clone-depth = 1
---------------------------------------------------

2)
clone repository to the specified location.

3)
chown portage:portage -R /var/lib/repos/gentoo-italia

